# .statbotignore — exclude files and folders from Statbot's context
# Syntax is like .gitignore: one pattern per line, # = comment
#
# Examples:
#   demo_code.*        ignore all demo_code files
#   statbot/           ignore the statbot source package folder
#   tests/             ignore the tests directory
#   *.egg-info         ignore build artifacts
#   node_modules/      ignore node_modules

# Uncomment the lines you want to activate:

# statbot/
# demo_code.*
# demo.py
# tests/
